From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jami <jami@jami.net>
Date: Tue, 21 Jul 2026 20:58:47 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] connectionmanager: ignore unauthenticated peer responses

DHT values may be delivered without a resolved owner certificate.  Ignore
those peer responses before the connection manager dereferences the owner
key while matching the response to pending connection attempts.
---
 src/connectionmanager.cpp | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/src/connectionmanager.cpp b/src/connectionmanager.cpp
index 0000000..0000000 100644
--- a/src/connectionmanager.cpp
+++ b/src/connectionmanager.cpp
@@ -1203,2 +1203,5 @@
+    if (!from)
+        return;
+
     auto peerId = from->getId();
     auto peerDeviceId = from->getLongId();
 
-- 
2.51.0
